{"tid":1409090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑警淫蟲強姦犯】扯高女學生衫見底衫、抽水摸女人波、天水圍除少女褲等等","createTime":"2019-08-04T19:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T22:06:03.000Z","uid":180201,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"39f115b44a41c0c84bdf56389919154d20bb0e7b","tid":1409090,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNP44ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNP44ce.png&h=d8df6b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chiBaTx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchiBaTx.png&h=d99e1ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抽水摸女人波片</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/617327131/posts/10155936255122132?s=100006481648084&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F617327131%2Fposts%2F10155936255122132%3Fs%3D100006481648084%26sfns%3Dmo&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=a86edf7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/617327131/posts/10155936255122132?s=100006481648084&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【元朗恐襲】白衣人鐵通狂毆兼借機捏胸 少女被打至骨折需縫針不敢報警</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360375</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLEwKcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLEwKcn.png&h=ee0d9853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重有無更多性侵/對女士造成精神/身體上傷害嘅新聞？唔好忘記之前嘅受害者！請支援！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b37a917d9c57cae4c161d270a897e9f765db3027","tid":1409090,"uid":180201,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUP8Mua.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUP8Mua.gif&h=5f783ea3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"765c0da6b53a528b34fc3ed6a7dbd7f0f5a89f5e","tid":1409090,"uid":157938,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:18:57.000Z","msg":"全民dm Emma Watson. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Femmawatson%3Figshid%3Db5y3xa4gke0u&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=22ede92e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u</a><br />\n<br />\nIG傳送門<br />\n<br />\nHello Emma,<br />\n<br />\nWe're writing to express concern over an incident involving the violation of female rights that has just happened in Hong Kong. As you may have noticed, Hong Kongers are currently experiencing police brutality on a daily basis during the process of fighting aginst the extradition bill imposed by the HK government. Earlier just now a female protestor was arrested near a local police station, during which her pants were violently ripped off against her will. The police officers made no attempt to protect her privacy which was unacceptable on any level. Since the beginning of the protests in June not one of our local feminist organizations have stood out for female rights. <br />\n<br />\nWe are in desperate times and sincerely seek your help in raising international concern over this matter as we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"117f378a8679f287d988f165c6ee1864c4c61b83","tid":1409090,"uid":235711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:19:09.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6570ead3374391b512748aa4e6df61fcbcc479","tid":1409090,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警係強姦犯，黑警